  "description": "<p><strong>在E3大展上微软宣布游戏主机上使用微软点可以转换成为当地的货币</strong>，此外这种方式也将成为Xbox Live未来主要的购买方式。鉴于这些改变微软表示将会对整个奖励系统进行调整。首先截至8月1日玩家不能通过Xbox Live Reward来获取微软点，以此为契机，微软将会更加完善整个奖励系统，为玩家提供更优秀的使用体验。<strong>玩家依然能够通过Xbox Live来获取相关的成就奖励，只是微软点被取消了。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e982933/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244527.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%82%B9%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88++8%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8BXbox+Live%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%96%E5%8A%B1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244527.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%82%B9%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88++8%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8BXbox+Live%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%96%E5%8A%B1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244527.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%82%B9%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88++8%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8BXbox+Live%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%96%E5%8A%B1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244527.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%82%B9%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88++8%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8BXbox+Live%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%96%E5%8A%B1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><